# Per-project tag formatter produces "release core 1.0.0" which contains
# spaces — invalid as a git ref. `releaseIOMonorepo check` runs `preflightTags`,
# which calls `validateTagName` on the resolved per-project tag and must reject
# it before any side effects.
-> releaseIOMonorepo check core release-version core=1.0.0 next-version core=1.1.0-SNAPSHOT

# Repo state must be untouched (check mode is read-only by definition; this
# also verifies no preflight side effects leaked).
> checkVersionUnchanged
> checkNoExtraCommits
> checkNoTags
